    • rational

      public static final Resource rational
      The owl:rational datatype supports lexical forms defined by the following grammar (whitespace within the grammar MUST be ignored and MUST NOT be included in the lexical forms of owl:rational, and single quotes are used to introduce terminal symbols): numerator '/' denominator
